 ('229', '279', 'en_us', 'Dillan Howell', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.00000', '0.00000', NULL, 'Dillan', 'Howell', 'Production Director and Global Executive Producer', NULL, 'DillanH@faithpromise.org', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'both', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '7', '0', NULL, '2017-09-01 16:42:38', '2017-09-01 18:27:27', '98393923-3970-4356-a7cd-71808a8f6ebd'),
 ('230', '280', 'en_us', 'Christy Cummings', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.00000', '0.00000', NULL, 'Christy', 'Cummings', 'fpKids Volunteer Coordinator', '<p>Christy was born and raised in north Knoxville.  After graduating from the University of Tennessee, she spent the next 18 years working with the Boys &amp; Girls Clubs of the Tennessee Valley as their Programs Specialist, developing, training, and supporting operational staff and volunteers.</p>\n\n<p>Christy comes to us from White Stone Church, and she has a heart for Haiti missions. She and her husband Rob were married in 1992.  They have been blessed with 3 beautiful girls, Savanna, Emma, and Bel.  Bel officially joined their family in September of 2012, from Jacmel, Haiti.</p>\n\n<p>Christy is delighted to be a part of the Family Ministry team and looks forward to all God has in store for her and her family at Faith Promise Church.</p>', 'ChristyC@faithpromise.org', '1204', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'both', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '7', '0', NULL, '2017-09-01 16:42:38', '2017-09-01 18:27:28', 'c4ea9ea0-455e-4dbe-83f9-142b3822c325'),
 ('231', '281', 'en_us', 'Robert Cunningham', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.00000', '0.00000', NULL, 'Robert', 'Cunningham', 'Anderson Interim Worship Coordinator', NULL, 'RobertC@faithpromise.org', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'both', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '7', '0', NULL, '2017-09-01 16:42:39', '2017-09-01 18:27:28', 'b89dcbce-7bcd-466a-a895-cb3d4dcf3b20'),
 ('232', '282', 'en_us', 'Ryan Silowski', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.00000', '0.00000', NULL, 'Ryan', 'Silowski', 'Anderson Campus Student Pastor', '<p>I was born in New Orleans, LA, and moved to east Tennessee in the early 2000\'s. I was home schooled for all twelve years of my primary education, and after high school I went to Johnson Bible College (now Johnson University).</p>\n\n<p>I graduated in 2013 with a Bachelors of Science in Biblical Studies and Digital Video Production. I have always had a love for storytelling, and video is the primary way we communicate stories in this day in age. I have loved films and filmmaking for some time.</p>\n\n<p>In college I spent two summers in Seattle, WA, and it quickly became a second home for me. In my senior year of college, I had the privilege to be a Director of Photography for a small Christian feature film made in the Knoxville area. I have also participated in several competitions for the Knoxville film festival.</p>\n\n<p>Through some of my internships in college, I became the Student Pastor at Life Point Church. In September of 2013, Life Point became a Faith Promise Campus, and I stayed on in my role of Student Pastor.</p>', 'RyanS@faithpromise.org', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'both', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '7', '0', NULL, '2017-09-01 16:42:39', '2017-09-01 18:27:28', '20701c13-1d9e-4a62-89d1-c2a6cc8ab078'),
