 ('274', '324', 'en_us', 'Brad Roberts', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.00000', '0.00000', NULL, 'Brad', 'Roberts', 'Web Developer', '<p>Hi! I\'m the web guy!</p>\n\n<p>My wife Amber and I have been married for {{ \"1998-09-05\" | age }} years and have 2 little ones, Matthew ({{ \"2009-11-01\" | age }}) and Kate ({{ \"2013-09-01\" | age }}). We\'ve been attending Faith Promise since 2007. The first time we visited I was blown away by how creative the service was. Amber wasn\'t sure about a pastor who wears jeans, but she came around.</p>\n\n<p>I grew up on Nintendo and skateboards and nearly 30 years later I\'m re-living my childhood playing The Legend of Zelda with my kids. My interest in web design started around 1999. Back then connecting to the Internet made <a href=\"https://www.dialupsound.com/\">this sound</a> and was billed by the hour. But, after seeing the possibilities of HTML I was hooked. I knew this is what I wanted to do for a living.</p>\n\n<p>Today I enjoy hanging out with my family and learning new web technologies. Some of my favorite things are <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mere-Christianity-C-S-Lewis/dp/0060652926\">Mere Christianity</a>, <a href=\"https://www.bible.com/bible/100/mat.5.nasb\">The Sermon on the Mount</a>, <a href=\"http://shoptalkshow.com\">Shop Talk Show</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.benjerry.com/flavors/chunky-monkey-ice-cream\">Ben &amp; Jerry\'s Chunky Monkey</a>.</p>\n\n<p>If you\'re a web developer, interested in web design, or maybe you just noticed something wrong with our website I\'d love to hear from you. You can find me on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bradsroberts\">Facebook</a>, on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bradsroberts\">Twitter</a>, or send me an <a href=\"mailto:bradr@faithpromise.org\">email</a>.</p>', 'BradR@faithpromise.org', NULL, 'bradsroberts', 'bradsroberts', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'both', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '7', '0', NULL, '2017-09-01 16:43:35', '2017-09-01 16:43:35', '15d03652-2785-4d68-9fc3-5ee148b724c2'),
