 ('277', '327', 'en_us', 'Vikki Huisman', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.00000', '0.00000', NULL, 'Vikki', 'Huisman', 'Assistant to the Executive Pastor', '<p>Vikki is the virtual assistant to Dr. Josh Whitehead. She has been married to Rick for over 20 years and they have three sons  Jacob (19), Josh (15) and Ben (9). Vikki is a lifelong resident of Illinois. When shes not driving to various high school marching band practices and performances, shes an avid reader who enjoys serving as a childrens ministry volunteer and writing book reviews.</p>', 'VikkiH@faithpromise.org', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'both', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '7', '0', NULL, '2017-09-01 16:43:38', '2017-09-01 16:43:38', 'bb3ca1f8-0004-4125-b1c2-69a804c9af54');
