 ('293', '343', 'en_us', 'Jennifer Corbin', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.00000', '0.00000', NULL, 'Jennifer', 'Corbin', 'Assistant to the North Knox Campus Pastor', '<p>Hi! I\'m Jennifer.</p>\n\n<p>I\'m originally from the Tri-Cities area. For nearly {{ \"2000-11-19\" | age }} years my husband has been an internal auditor for TVA, which is how we ended up living in Knoxville. We\'ve been married for {{ \"2004-11-18\" | age }} years, met at Carson Newman, and have two daughters, Olivia - {{ \"2010-11-18\" | age }} and Abigail - {{ \"2013-11-18\" | age }}. We also have a weiner dog named Peanut. He\'s our little old man - he\'s almost 16 years old.</p>', 'jenniferc@faithpromise.org', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'both', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '7', '0', NULL, '2017-09-01 16:44:00', '2017-09-01 16:44:00', '0401be52-bd02-4a89-a112-a63cd2c112f3'),
