 ('237', '324', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Brad Roberts\",\"slug\":\"brad-roberts\",\"postDate\":1439933612,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"<p>Hi! I\'m the web guy!<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>My wife Amber and I have been married for {{ \\\"1998-09-05\\\" | age }} years and have 2 little ones, Matthew ({{ \\\"2009-11-01\\\" | age }}) and Kate ({{ \\\"2013-09-01\\\" | age }}). We\'ve been attending Faith Promise since 2007. The first time we visited I was blown away by how creative the service was. Amber wasn\'t sure about a pastor who wears jeans, but she came around.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>I grew up on Nintendo and skateboards and nearly 30 years later I\'m re-living my childhood playing The Legend of Zelda with my kids. My interest in web design started around 1999. Back then connecting to the Internet made <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.dialupsound.com\\/\\\">this sound<\\/a> and was billed by the hour. But, after seeing the possibilities of HTML I was hooked. I knew this is what I wanted to do for a living.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Today I enjoy hanging out with my family and learning new web technologies. Some of my favorite things are <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Mere-Christianity-C-S-Lewis\\/dp\\/0060652926\\\">Mere Christianity<\\/a>, <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bible.com\\/bible\\/100\\/mat.5.nasb\\\">The Sermon on the Mount<\\/a>, <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/shoptalkshow.com\\\">Shop Talk Show<\\/a>, and <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.benjerry.com\\/flavors\\/chunky-monkey-ice-cream\\\">Ben &amp; Jerry\'s Chunky Monkey<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>If you\'re a web developer, interested in web design, or maybe you just noticed something wrong with our website I\'d love to hear from you. You can find me on <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/bradsroberts\\\">Facebook<\\/a>, on <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/bradsroberts\\\">Twitter<\\/a>, or send me an <a href=\\\"&#109;&#97;&#x69;l&#116;&#x6f;&#x3a;&#98;&#114;&#x61;&#x64;&#114;&#64;&#x66;a&#105;&#x74;&#x68;&#112;&#114;&#x6f;&#x6d;&#105;&#115;&#x65;.&#111;&#x72;&#x67;\\\">email<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"BradR@faithpromise.org\",\"23\":\"bradsroberts\",\"16\":\"Brad\",\"19\":\"Web Developer\",\"17\":\"Roberts\",\"26\":[\"27\"],\"27\":[],\"24\":\"bradsroberts\"}}', '2017-09-01 16:43:36', '2017-09-01 16:43:36', 'c42b647a-b3a0-4bca-a8b4-0c724e3bd443'),
