 ('242', '333', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Levi Trentham\",\"slug\":\"levi-trentham\",\"postDate\":1447956466,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"<p>Hello, I have been attending Faith Promise for over five years. It was a big change coming from a small baptist church, but it didn\'t take long for me to realize how special of a place FP is. I am very grateful and blessed to be a part of the operations team and I am excited to contribute to the future of FP! I am married to Darah Trentham and we will be going on two years in March. Please email me if interested in serving such as setting up for events, etc. God Bless!<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"levit@faithpromise.org\",\"16\":\"Levi\",\"19\":\"Facilities Associate\",\"17\":\"Trentham\",\"26\":[\"28\"],\"27\":[]}}', '2017-09-01 16:43:47', '2017-09-01 16:43:47', '1c68e791-5bc6-4c6e-8322-2fd8f7145ecd'),
