 ('356', '263', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Zach Carringer\",\"slug\":\"zach-carringer\",\"postDate\":1439933611,\"expiryDate\":1493787600,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"21\":\"ZachC@faithpromise.org\",\"23\":\"ZachCarringer\",\"16\":\"Zach\",\"25\":\"zachcarringer\",\"19\":\"Director of Audio & Lighting\",\"17\":\"Carringer\",\"26\":[\"27\"],\"24\":\"zachcarringer\"}}', '2017-09-01 18:27:18', '2017-09-01 18:27:18', 'de5d1173-b143-4794-a924-69735ed61841'),
 ('357', '265', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Tonja Breaux\",\"slug\":\"tonja-breaux\",\"postDate\":1439933611,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"14\":[\"128\"],\"21\":\"TonjaB@faithpromise.org\",\"23\":\"tonja.breaux\",\"16\":\"Tonja\",\"25\":\"thetonj\",\"19\":\"Farragut Campus Administrative Assistant\",\"17\":\"Breaux\",\"26\":[\"28\"],\"22\":\"1305\",\"27\":[\"481\"]}}', '2017-09-01 18:27:22', '2017-09-01 18:27:22', '59240672-6c86-4d3d-9855-2226741d0063'),
 ('358', '267', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Dustin Scott\",\"slug\":\"dustin-scott\",\"postDate\":1439933611,\"expiryDate\":1501736400,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"14\":[\"6\"],\"21\":\"DustinS@faithpromise.org\",\"23\":\"dustin.scott24\",\"16\":\"Dustin\",\"19\":\"Pastor of Group Leader Discipleship\",\"17\":\"Scott\",\"26\":[\"26\"],\"22\":\"1302\"}}', '2017-09-01 18:27:23', '2017-09-01 18:27:23', '656f9c88-c9bc-42ec-9aea-56707cb2846d'),
 ('359', '269', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Mallory Ellis\",\"slug\":\"mallory-ellis\",\"postDate\":1439933611,\"expiryDate\":1503378000,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"<p>Mallory has been on staff since 2012. She has a degree in Accounting from UT and loves being able to use her degree in ministry at Faith Promise.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>She has a passion to serve those who serve. She loves being able to work with the church staff and support them and encourage them as they grow. She feels incredibly blessed to be a part of Faith Promise at this level.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Mallory has been married to Mike since 2009 and they were blessed with a wonderful daughter, Nora in January 2015.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Mallory?s favorite place to travel to is NYC. She loves watching movies, baking, reading, hiking and traveling.<\\/p>\",\"14\":[\"6\"],\"21\":\"MalloryE@faithpromise.org\",\"23\":\"mallory.a.ellis.7\",\"16\":\"Mallory\",\"25\":\"malloryaellis\",\"19\":\"Finance & Human Resources Director\",\"17\":\"Ellis\",\"26\":[\"28\"],\"22\":\"1603\",\"24\":\"malloryellis\"}}', '2017-09-01 18:27:23', '2017-09-01 18:27:23', 'ff8b25e3-23c8-4cdc-8f19-6a3e67f30eda'),
 ('360', '271', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Macy Scarbrough\",\"slug\":\"macy-scarbrough\",\"postDate\":1439933611,\"expiryDate\":1451928878,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"<p>Hi! My name is Macy Scarbrough, and I\'ve been on staff at Faith Promise since June of 2012. I grew up in church, and have had a relationship with the Lord since an early age. I was even blessed enough to have Miles Creasman, our Next Steps Pastor\\/Blount Campus Groups Pastor, as my youth pastor while growing up!<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>I also volunteer in <a href=\\\"\\/fpkids\\\">fpKids<\\/a>, our children\'s ministry, and have loved giving children the opportunity to learn about the Lord. I am so excited about the plans that God has for Faith Promise Church and spreading His Word, and I am thankful to be a part of it!<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>I\'ve lived in Knoxville for 20 years and have been married to my high school sweetheart for a little over a year now. I graduated from Bearden High School, graduated from UT with a degree in Psychology and Child and Family Studies, and am now finishing up nursing school at Carson Newman. It\\u2019s been a long road discovering God\\u2019s plan for my career, but I can\\u2019t wait to serve others in the nursing field once I graduate.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Outside of school, I enjoy spending time with my family and friends. I also love seeing movies, Coca Cola, board games, Disneyworld, Italian food, traveling, and being a cat mom to my kitten Nala.<\\/p>\",\"14\":[\"6\"],\"21\":\"MacyD@faithpromise.org\",\"23\":\"macy.deel\",\"16\":\"Macy\",\"25\":\"mscarbrough52\",\"19\":\"Next Steps Assistant\",\"17\":\"Scarbrough\",\"26\":[\"28\",\"26\",\"30\"],\"22\":\"1711\",\"24\":\"MacyDeel\"}}', '2017-09-01 18:27:24', '2017-09-01 18:27:24', '40934f7f-9b49-4921-9eb9-3ab466a919ff'),
 ('361', '272', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Holly Wallace\",\"slug\":\"holly-wallace\",\"postDate\":1439933611,\"expiryDate\":1371826972,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"<p>Holly grew up in High Point, North Carolina, and graduated from Liberty University. Upon graduation, Holly married her high school sweetheart, Michael, and they moved to Texas. While in Texas, Holly worked at Fellowship Church as the Middle School Ministry Coordinator of Volunteers.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>In December of 2009 Michael and Holly moved back east for Michael to be the High School Pastor at Faith Promise Church, Pellissippi Campus. After the move, Holly became a stay-at-home mom for their two children, Colton and Emory.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Holly is driven by the fact that spending one intentional hour a week with a child can change their life. She loves children and is excited about the opportunity to make a difference in the life of a Kids Hope child this school year.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>You can connect with Holly via <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/holly.wallace.31\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Facebook<\\/a>, <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/hollyewallace\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Twitter<\\/a> or <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/pinterest.com\\/hollywallace\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Pinterest<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"KidsHope@faithpromise.org\",\"16\":\"Holly\",\"19\":\"Kids Hope Director\",\"17\":\"Wallace\"}}', '2017-09-01 18:27:24', '2017-09-01 18:27:24', '9ffe7fee-6c20-41d0-84c4-ee8602d3bf06'),
 ('362', '274', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Chad Funk\",\"slug\":\"chad-funk\",\"postDate\":1439933611,\"expiryDate\":1453480298,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"<p>Chad was born and raised in Iowa. In 1997 he married his wife Brandi, and they have a daughter named Taylor. After a seventeen-year battle with strongholds, Chad gave his life to Jesus in December of 2006. Since that time he has been radically pursuing the Lord. Chad and his family made the move Tennessee in the summer of 2008 for his job. Chad and his family have been attending Faith Promise since 2009.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Chad has a background in mechanical contracting and worked in that field for over fifteen years. In the fall of 2009 Chad felt God was taking him in a different direction, and in December of 2011 he graduated from Liberty University. Chad is excited about the opportunity that God has given him to serve in full-time ministry and can\'t wait to see what God has planned!<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Chad enjoys hanging out with his family and friends. He also enjoys mild running (close to mall walking). He loves cookies and is a huge fan of the Green Bay Packers. Go Pack Go!<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>Connect with Chad on <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/chadjfunk\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Twitter<\\/a>, <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/chad.funk.3\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Facebook<\\/a>, or <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/chadjfunk.com\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">his blog<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"14\":[\"15\"],\"21\":\"ChadF@faithpromise.org\",\"23\":\"chad.funk.3\",\"16\":\"Chad\",\"19\":\"Campbell Campus Pastor & fpCelebrate Director\",\"17\":\"Funk\",\"26\":[\"23\",\"31\"],\"22\":\"1410\",\"24\":\"chadjfunk\"}}', '2017-09-01 18:27:25', '2017-09-01 18:27:25', 'c4ef1469-ec1f-4b32-9092-c46398aae467'),
 ('363', '275', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Jeff Rose\",\"slug\":\"jeff-rose\",\"postDate\":1439933611,\"expiryDate\":1439933624,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"<p>Jeff has been a member of FPC since the very beginning of the church, and has served in various areas before joining the staff in September 2012. Jeff\'s background includes Maintenance Supervisor for the Boys &amp; Girls Club of TN Valley. He loves sports, traveling, and action movies.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>He and his wife Robyn live in the Hardin Valley area with their two dogs Sophie and Charlie. They have one daughter, Jennifer, who is also on FPC staff as Assistant to the Pastor of Family Ministries.<\\/p>\",\"14\":[\"6\"],\"21\":\"JeffR@faithpromise.org\",\"16\":\"Jeff\",\"19\":\"Building Services Director\",\"17\":\"Rose\",\"26\":[\"28\"],\"22\":\"1703\"}}', '2017-09-01 18:27:26', '2017-09-01 18:27:26', '049e7696-540c-4b03-8c41-1561425cefaa'),
