 ('439', '542', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Tony Giordano\",\"slug\":\"tony-giordano\",\"postDate\":1443544970,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"<p>Hey!<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>I moved to Tennessee from Florida in August 2014 and have loved it here ever since. The 24\\/7 year round heat of Florida got tiresome after 15 years, so I needed a change! My fianc\\u00e9 (Kate) and I first attended Faith Promise on Easter of 2014, and we fell in love with the Church instantly. I received my B.A.S. Degree in Technology Management in December of 2015, and married my beautiful wife in May of 2016!<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>When I was growing up I was a video game enthusiast, which is what got me interested in computers. I still enjoy playing video games occasionally, but I am mainly a technology geek now. I love building computers, researching computer components, and looking at new technologies in my free time. I also enjoy reading, and watching Ice Hockey in my spare time as well. Go <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/lightning.nhl.com\\/club\\/index.htm\\\">Lightning<\\/a>!<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>I know God meant for me to move to Tennessee because I would have never had an opportunity like this in Florida. I am so thankful for all the staff at Faith Promise for making this church feel like a family, and I am extremely happy to be able to call it my home church.<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"TonyG@faithpromise.org\",\"23\":\"tony.giordano.5458\",\"16\":\"Tony\",\"19\":\"IT Associate\",\"17\":\"Giordano\",\"26\":[\"28\"],\"27\":[\"483\"],\"24\":\"Tgiordano92\"}}', '2017-09-01 18:41:26', '2017-09-01 18:41:26', '5a0bf56d-2b12-4644-b222-76ca663be995'),
 ('440', '543', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Sara Fulton\",\"slug\":\"sara-fulton\",\"postDate\":1439933611,\"expiryDate\":1480399200,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"<p>My name is Sara Fulton, and my family and I have been attending Faith Promise since 2011. I am originally from Atlanta, GA, and I have been living in Knoxville since 2003 when I moved here for college.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>I have had a passion for counseling and reaching out to others since I was a child. I graduated with my Bachelor\'s from Johnson University and my Master\'s from Argosy University. I am hoping to obtain my license in professional counseling in the next few years and will one day return to school to obtain my Ph.D. My goal is to gain all that I can in order to best serve those that I work with. My desire is to love God and to serve others to His glory and purpose.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>My husband and I have been married for five years and we have a beautiful daughter who is almost two. We have three crazy dogs and love animals. We love to be outdoors and spending time with family and friends.<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"SaraF@faithpromise.org\",\"16\":\"Sara\",\"19\":\"Staff Counselor\",\"17\":\"Fulton\",\"26\":[\"28\",\"31\"]}}', '2017-09-01 18:41:26', '2017-09-01 18:41:26', 'cc2c38b9-b9cd-4223-94c5-fbc83c96f110'),
