 ('250', 'field', '20', 'en_us', ' hi i m shannan i am originally from the sf bay area in california but after high school i joined a touring ministry team based in knoxville where i met my husband nick the lord has kept us here since then and led us to faith promise where we are so excited to serve i have been at faith promise since 2008 the same year nick and i were married with my music background i immediately became involved in the worship ministry as a volunteer and eventually became a volunteer worship leader i was brought on staff in 2010 to fill in as the assistant to the worship and creative arts director which through a series of events led to a permanent position as the worship administrative assistant i am a student at liberty university online earning my degree in biblical studies with a minor in christian counseling my husband nick is also a student at tennessee temple university online earning his degree in biblical studies with a minor in intercultural studies missions we are so excited to finally be done soon as i will graduate this may of 2011 and he ll be done in december but then it s seminary for him interesting fact four months after nick and i were married we headed overseas with the international mission board and served in lisbon portugal for eight months and worked with youth partnering with young life international we both love traveling and ministry and have big hearts for missions '),
